Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [By reporter Zhang Huanli (1728 3562 0448)] </F>
  [Text] Fukuoka, 3 Mar (XINHUA) -- Vice Premier Zhu Rongji 
and his party called on the staff of the Chinese Consulate 
General in Fukuoka, Japan, this evening. 
