<H3> <TI>   Aliyev Leaves for Shanghai </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  OW0903094094 Beijing XINHUA in English 0825 GMT 9 Mar 94 </F>
<F P=103> OW0903094094 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Beijing, March 9 (XINHUA) -- Geydar Aliyev, 
president of Azerbaijan, and his party left here for Shanghai by 
special plane today. 
  The Azerbaijan guests were accompanied by Yin Dakui, 
chairman 
of the Chinese Government Reception Committee and vice minister 
of public health. 
  In a speech delivered this morning at the Chinese Academy of 
Social Sciences (CASS), Aliyev briefed his listeners on the 
domestic situation and foreign policies of Azerbaijan. 
  Aliyev was warmly welcomed by CASS President Hu Sheng. 
  President Aliyev held a press conference here yesterday 
evening. 

</TEXT>

