Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Beijing, March (XINHUA) -- Chinese women from all 
walks of life are called on to make even greater contributions 
to peaceful unification and the prosperity of the country. 
  Lei Jieqiong, vice-chairwoman of the Standing Committee of 
China's National People's Congress, made the call at a forum 
