Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Shanghai, March 6 (XINHUA) -- China is to send more 
personnel for training abroad to serve the country's reform and 
opening to the outside world. 
  This was disclosed here recently at a meeting jointly 
sponsored by the State Commission for Restructuring the Economy 
and the State Bureau of Foreign Experts Affairs. 
